         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Bot Garden 6/4/71 ¶  ¶ Allow me, dear Mr Fitzgibbon, to draw your kind attention to the defective state of the fences from the Barracks to Prince's Bridge. The cattle from the flat come across the roa...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.04.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edmund FitzGibbon</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 527, unit 734, VPRS 3181/P Town Clerk's file series 1, VA 511 Melbourne, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS file annotation: 'Ansd'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Bot Garden 6/4/71</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Allow me, dear Mr Fitzgibbon, to draw your kind attention to the defective state of the fences from the Barracks to Prince's Bridge. The cattle from the flat come across the road and whenever by any negligence a gate is left open in my reserve, I have a horde of invading quadrupeds amusing themselves among my trees and requiring the united efforts of many nimble persons to drive them out of their elysium.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As I am so reduced in funds of the Department, and can ill spare any one away from his work, I hope you will have pity on me.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I will send my contribution to you soon for the French fund.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">During the Franco-Prussian War funds for the relief of wounded soldiers<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">widows, orphans<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">distressed civilians of both sides were opened in Victoria.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">It is not known what role FitzGibbon played, no</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">r</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">which of the funds that existed</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M is referring. At a meeting convened by W A Brahe, Consul in Melbourne for the North German Federatiion, M was elected to a Committee for 'raising a fund to assist the soldiers wounded in the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">p</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">resent war with France, and the widows and orohans of thse who may be killed' (</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne) 5 September p. 3)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">. M was not alone in supporting funds for relief of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">either</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>French and German</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>victims</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">, see, for example, the account of a German present at the meeting of the 'French residents in Melbourne' held on 30 September 1870 (</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne), 1 October 1870, p. 2)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
